race.comment: MYTHOLOGY (12) failed to sprint with then in the straight when a plugging fifth on debut over 1100m at Gosford. Looking for this trip and should handle the going. HUSH HUSH (11) resumes from a lengthy spell and fitted with the two trials. Ploughed through the heavy going on debut when a battling second over 1100m at Warwick Farm last August. Expected to go close. GO GLENN (5) has a fitness edge over these fourth-up and will handle the going. On the quick backup after holding on to run second over 1200m at Gosford in a Super Mdn. Gets his chance in the small field. FIERCE CRITIC (9) Fierce Impact filly from Latina Beauty on debut for the Matt Smith yard. Latest trials have been fair and look for her closing late.
